    "lines": [
      "# Storage Engine Interview",
      "",
      "The storage engine uses write-ahead logging, 中文写前日志, to recover committed writes after failure.",
      "",
      "## Operational Detail",
      "",
      "存储引擎访谈说明 checkpoint 只缩短重放范围，不替代 WAL。",
      "",
      "## Aliases",
      "",
      "Prewrite journal, WAL, and 预写式日志 refer to the durable intent record in this discussion.",
      "",
      "## Limits",
      "",
      "Recovery is fail-closed when the log sequence contains a gap."
    ],
